info.author: Einar Birnir Olafsson
info.name: spacr
info.summary: Spatial phenotype analysis of crisp screens (SpaCr). A collection of functions for generating cellpose masks -> single object images and measurements -> annotation and classification of single object images. Spacr uses batch normalization to facilitate accurate segmentation of objects with low foreground representation.
